# Auto push

When the user asks for a code change and the work is complete:

1. Commit with a clear message (follow git safety protocol).
2. Push to `origin/main` automatically — do not wait for them to say "push".

Skip auto push only if they say not to push, ask for review first, or the work is intentionally incomplete/WIP.

After push, briefly confirm commit hash and that Vercel will deploy.
